WEBVTT

1
00:00:01.558 --> 00:00:03.883
I want my Huang... I won't let it go.

2
00:00:05.427 --> 00:00:06.918
I want my Huang...

3
00:00:07.163 --> 00:00:08.860
I want my Huang... I won't let it go.

4
00:00:09.100 --> 00:00:10.196
Gui...

5
00:00:16.875 --> 00:00:21.871
Gui. you are too young to understand.

6
00:00:22.680 --> 00:00:25.675
Huang leaves this world in peace.

7
00:00:25.816 --> 00:00:28.751
since he had done what he needed to do.

8
00:00:29.020 --> 00:00:31.720
Everyone dies.

9
00:00:32.022 --> 00:00:33.649
So does Huang.

10
00:00:34.001 --> 00:00:36.793
but one only leaves in peace

11
00:00:37.000 --> 00:00:40.531
when there is no regret in one's life.

12
00:00:40.865 --> 00:00:42.429
Don't cry. my boy.

13
00:00:44.000 --> 00:00:50.074
Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

14
00:01:21.171 --> 00:01:24.106
Gui has a problem!

15
00:01:24.343 --> 00:01:26.332
What happened to him?

16
00:01:28.012 --> 00:01:29.874
He missed his bull so much

17
00:01:30.147 --> 00:01:32.377
that he stole one from the Siam clan.

18
00:01:32.449 --> 00:01:33.848
He got caught over there

19
00:01:35.352 --> 00:01:38.446
and they are about to punish him
according to their law.

20
00:01:38.855 --> 00:01:42.155
Let's go to save Gui!

21
00:01:52.437 --> 00:01:54.928
Help me...

22
00:01:56.474 --> 00:01:57.338
Help me...

23
00:01:57.408 --> 00:01:58.432
Beat him.

24
00:02:03.414 --> 00:02:05.279
Help me...

25
00:02:06.951 --> 00:02:08.316
help me...

26
00:02:11.088 --> 00:02:13.083
Help me...

27
00:02:13.458 --> 00:02:16.188
Are you coming for a fight?

28
00:02:17.461 --> 00:02:20.919
Gui made a mistake and should be punished.

29
00:02:21.331 --> 00:02:23.390
You have already punished him enough.

30
00:02:24.634 --> 00:02:28.367
I'm here to make a formal apology.

31
00:02:30.141 --> 00:02:32.709
The boy doesn't know any better.

32
00:02:33.077 --> 00:02:35.710
Let us take him back.

33
00:02:36.000 --> 00:02:39.248
Indeed he is a child.

34
00:02:39.550 --> 00:02:42.044
But even for children in our village.

35
00:02:42.352 --> 00:02:45.180
we beat them for the burning time
of an incense

36
00:02:45.489 --> 00:02:48.155
so they will remember the lesson.

37
00:02:48.392 --> 00:02:50.750
Go on. Beat him.

38
00:02:53.098 --> 00:02:53.587
Help me!

39
00:02:53.899 --> 00:02:58.024
The child can't take it.
Let me take the beating for him!

40
00:02:58.203 --> 00:02:59.295
Stop!

41
00:03:09.682 --> 00:03:12.377
Let me take the beatings for Gui.

42
00:03:14.219 --> 00:03:17.046
Well. this punishment is for children.

43
00:03:21.260 --> 00:03:24.052
Adults should be punished in another way.

44
00:03:26.031 --> 00:03:26.896
How?

45
00:03:32.003 --> 00:03:34.164
Take on my iron fist.

46
00:03:37.000 --> 00:03:41.071
If I am still standing
when this incense burns out.

47
00:03:41.312 --> 00:03:44.940
you will have to release the child.

48
00:03:47.651 --> 00:03:50.711
Sure! No argument about life and death?

49
00:03:52.490 --> 00:03:53.650
No argument!

50
00:03:55.193 --> 00:03:56.690
It's settled then?

51
00:03:57.395 --> 00:03:58.521
Yes.

52
00:04:20.118 --> 00:04:22.349
Grandma. what's wrong with him?

53
00:04:50.047 --> 00:04:51.572
Ox. Ox!

54
00:04:55.486 --> 00:04:57.386
You don't want to hurt others.

55
00:04:58.156 --> 00:05:00.590
but you should let others hurt you.

56
00:05:01.000 --> 00:05:01.784
son!

57
00:05:02.029 --> 00:05:05.427
How can we stand this! Let's help him.

58
00:05:08.033 --> 00:05:08.957
Stop!

59
00:05:09.534 --> 00:05:10.266
Stop!

60
00:05:15.607 --> 00:05:17.538
The incense is still burning.

61
00:05:48.973 --> 00:05:51.139
Stand up. stand up...

62
00:05:51.577 --> 00:05:53.538
Keep beating... beat him.

63
00:05:56.613 --> 00:06:00.413
The incense has burnt out.
You lose. you lose...

64
00:06:04.856 --> 00:06:05.888
Let him go!

65
00:06:09.394 --> 00:06:10.925
Let's go home. Gui. Go.

66
00:06:54.205 --> 00:06:55.805
Time to go home.

67
00:06:56.574 --> 00:06:58.500
I want to stay a little longer with Ox.

68
00:06:58.878 --> 00:07:00.135
I don't go home.

69
00:07:00.545 --> 00:07:01.839
Gui. aren't you hungry?

70
00:07:02.080 --> 00:07:04.113
Are you not hungry? Ox might be hungry.

71
00:07:04.315 --> 00:07:05.604
No. I am not hungry.

72
00:07:05.850 --> 00:07:07.849
I can stay here a little longer with Gui.

73
00:07:08.052 --> 00:07:09.076
Ox. you are the best.

74
00:07:09.521 --> 00:07:11.048
So what does that make me?

75
00:07:15.092 --> 00:07:16.284
Aunt Moon.

76
00:07:16.461 --> 00:07:18.894
can you ask Ox a favor for me?

77
00:07:19.164 --> 00:07:21.195
You and Ox are so close.

78
00:07:21.432 --> 00:07:23.126
why do you need my help?

79
00:07:23.300 --> 00:07:25.498
Because. you are the dearest to Ox.

80
00:07:27.505 --> 00:07:30.804
Gui. Don't talk nonsense.

81
00:07:31.876 --> 00:07:34.243
Gui. you can ask me yourself.

82
00:07:34.713 --> 00:07:36.578
You keep refusing to teach me martial arts.
but I really want to learn.

83
00:07:36.848 --> 00:07:37.842
I also want to learn!

84
00:07:38.684 --> 00:07:39.241
Gui. why do you want

85
00:07:39.484 --> 00:07:40.815
to learn martial arts?

86
00:07:41.219 --> 00:07:42.777
So the others won't bully me.

87
00:07:43.555 --> 00:07:44.419
What about you?

88
00:07:44.656 --> 00:07:45.918
I want everyone to be afraid of me.

89
00:07:46.625 --> 00:07:48.217
What if Ning bullies you. what will you do?

90
00:07:48.460 --> 00:07:49.688
I will hit him back

91
00:07:50.729 --> 00:07:52.492
What about you. will you fight Gui back?

92
00:07:52.731 --> 00:07:54.722
For sure.
I will fight Gui until he's scared of me.

93
00:07:54.900 --> 00:07:55.964
What if you can't beat him?

94
00:07:56.101 --> 00:07:57.828
Then. I will learn from a master

95
00:07:58.737 --> 00:07:59.669
Then what will you do?

96
00:07:59.771 --> 00:08:01.864
I will learn from a master

97
00:08:02.274 --> 00:08:03.741
and then fight him again.

98
00:08:05.677 --> 00:08:07.645
You beat him up. and he beats you up.

99
00:08:07.746 --> 00:08:09.873
When will this end?

100
00:08:15.220 --> 00:08:17.450
It's not that I don't want to teach you.

101
00:08:17.790 --> 00:08:19.690
I also need to think about

102
00:08:20.026 --> 00:08:21.484
why we learn martial arts.

103
00:08:24.363 --> 00:08:26.888
Let's go and catch the dragonflies!

104
00:09:15.447 --> 00:09:16.379
Grandma. let's eat.

105
00:09:16.581 --> 00:09:17.143
Ok.

106
00:09:24.423 --> 00:09:25.390
Grandma

107
00:09:25.757 --> 00:09:28.021
- Moon...
- Yes. Grandma.

108
00:09:29.294 --> 00:09:31.854
In a few days.

109
00:09:32.097 --> 00:09:35.828
we should visit your parents' graves.

110
00:09:36.468 --> 00:09:37.166
Ok.

111
00:09:45.911 --> 00:09:46.707
I am going to...

112
00:09:46.878 --> 00:09:48.837
visit my parents' graves.

113
00:10:01.326 --> 00:10:02.486
Hey. Ox.

114
00:11:13.632 --> 00:11:14.564
Have a drink of water.

115
00:11:21.873 --> 00:11:23.431
Can we talk?

116
00:11:26.211 --> 00:11:27.371
You are leaving...

117
00:11:33.018 --> 00:11:34.144
I was thinking...

118
00:11:34.786 --> 00:11:36.413
maybe I should visit my parents' graves.

119
00:11:38.523 --> 00:11:40.889
You should go. Family is important.

120
00:12:27.239 --> 00:12:28.797
I'll come back soon.

121
00:12:34.946 --> 00:12:36.504
You've been here for many years.

122
00:12:37.048 --> 00:12:40.779
Yet I've always known
one day you will leave.

123
00:12:42.053 --> 00:12:43.042
The truth is. I...

124
00:12:53.965 --> 00:12:57.662
Take these clean clothes for your trip.

125
00:13:02.207 --> 00:13:04.141
You don't even know my real name.

126
00:13:06.544 --> 00:13:07.772
You don't have to tell me.

127
00:13:08.713 --> 00:13:11.147
I don't need to know where you're from...

128
00:13:12.017 --> 00:13:13.211
or where you're going.

129
00:13:14.619 --> 00:13:15.553
You will always be "Ox" to me.

130
00:13:22.694 --> 00:13:24.286
My name is Huo Yuanjia.

131
00:14:06.671 --> 00:14:08.002
I'll always remember.

132
00:15:40.198 --> 00:15:43.759
Late Qing Dynasty

133
00:15:45.069 --> 00:15:48.002
Various strong countries invaded China

134
00:15:49.107 --> 00:15:52.372
Tianjin became partly colonized

135
00:16:18.336 --> 00:16:20.360
Believe in God.
and you'll have everlasting life.

136
00:16:20.471 --> 00:16:22.037
...his words are written here.

137
00:16:22.207 --> 00:16:23.198
God's words...

138
00:16:52.036 --> 00:16:53.098
Huo Yuanjia!

139
00:16:54.271 --> 00:16:55.796
Champion of Tianjin!

140
00:16:56.040 --> 00:16:57.200
Huo Yuanjia!

141
00:16:58.510 --> 00:17:01.240
Champion of Tianjin! Huo Yuanjia!

142
00:17:03.248 --> 00:17:06.115
Huo Yuanjia has returned to the ring.

143
00:17:08.353 --> 00:17:10.753
Huo Yuanjia has returned to the ring.

144
00:17:56.100 --> 00:17:57.897
- Young master!
- Lai!

145
00:17:58.136 --> 00:17:59.160
You've finally returned!

146
00:17:59.404 --> 00:18:00.234
Good. good...

147
00:18:00:305 --> 00:18:01.533
Let me take your bag.

148
00:18:33.271 --> 00:18:36.138
Please forgive me...

149
00:18:36.474 --> 00:18:38.999
it was not easy maintaining this house.

150
00:19:01.666 --> 00:19:03.432
I did my best...

151
00:19:04.237 --> 00:19:06.329
trying to keep everything...

152
00:19:06.572 --> 00:19:08.199
the way it was.

153
00:19:12.010 --> 00:19:13.375
It must have been very hard for you.

154
00:19:14.178 --> 00:19:15.577
I'm sorry for not doing better.

155
00:19:16.280 --> 00:19:17.338
Young Master.

156
00:19:17.415 --> 00:19:18.882
After you left...

157
00:19:19.317 --> 00:19:22.150
the creditors came... to collect money.

158
00:19:22.553 --> 00:19:24.043
tearing this place...

159
00:19:24.389 --> 00:19:27.017
apart.

160
00:19:27.558 --> 00:19:31.392
The house was almost foreclosed.

161
00:19:31.464 --> 00:19:35.864
We would have lost...

162
00:19:36.200 --> 00:19:37.599
everything...

163
00:19:38.269 --> 00:19:41.397
but someone sent money.

164
00:19:42.440 --> 00:19:44.305
I later figured...

165
00:19:44.676 --> 00:19:48.612
it was your good friend Mr. Nong Jinsun.

166
00:20:02.927 --> 00:20:04.451
I don't need these anymore.

167
00:20:07.165 --> 00:20:08.097
Neither do...

168
00:20:08.332 --> 00:20:09.959
my parents.

169
00:20:15.004 --> 00:20:15.836
Father...

170
00:20:16.107 --> 00:20:17.369
I...

171
00:20:17.809 --> 00:20:19.376
finally realized...

172
00:20:20.979 --> 00:20:24.447
