173
00:20:26.050 --> 00:20:29.213
You are the true Champion.

174
00:20:30.621 --> 00:20:32.020
Mother.

175
00:20:32.590 --> 00:20:35.388
you taught me how to be a good person.

176
00:20:37.061 --> 00:20:39.495
I was too arrogant to understand.

177
00:20:43.434 --> 00:20:44.366
Rest assured

178
00:20:44.535 --> 00:20:47.299
I will not disappoint you again.

179
00:20:54.312 --> 00:20:55.279
My dear Jade.

180
00:20:56.514 --> 00:20:59.608
I was not a good father.

181
00:21:01.452 --> 00:21:04.545
And because of me.
you suffered a horrible death.

182
00:21:06.024 --> 00:21:09.958
I was never good enough for you.

183
00:21:45.229 --> 00:21:46.321
Let's have tea.

184
00:22:04.148 --> 00:22:05.581
Sir. I am sorry.

185
00:22:05.850 --> 00:22:07.249
My boss does not want to see you.

186
00:22:07.485 --> 00:22:09.146
but he wants you to have this.

187
00:22:34.445 --> 00:22:36.414
Watch your way.

188
00:22:39.417 --> 00:22:42.318
Leave a way. Excuse me...

189
00:23:03.574 --> 00:23:07.510
Mrs. Chin. I am very sorry
for what I have done.

190
00:23:08.713 --> 00:23:11.648
Please allow me to pay my respects.

191
00:23:29.333 --> 00:23:31.494
Mother. Mother.

192
00:23:58.629 --> 00:23:59.926
Get out and kneel down.

193
00:24:01.267 --> 00:24:03.201
You'll gonna have a hard time
if you come again

194
00:24:03.369 --> 00:24:05.167
You dare to come with no money?

195
00:24:06.200 --> 00:24:06.729
Get away!

196
00:24:06.871 --> 00:24:08.703
Don't come again
or you'll have a hard time.

197
00:24:08.900 --> 00:24:09.638
Get away! Get away!

198
00:24:16.647 --> 00:24:17.671
Master...

199
00:24:18.916 --> 00:24:19.644
Master...

200
00:24:20.184 --> 00:24:20.841
Master...

201
00:24:20.999 --> 00:24:23.445
- Master. we are sorry!
- we are sorry!

202
00:24:24.422 --> 00:24:26.616
Master. I learned kung fu
with you since I was a child.

203
00:24:26.924 --> 00:24:29.222
I don't know another

204
00:24:29.560 --> 00:24:31.960
way to making a living.

205
00:24:32.797 --> 00:24:34.958
Now you are back. and...

206
00:24:36.500 --> 00:24:37.762
Master. please forgive us!

207
00:24:38.669 --> 00:24:39.693
Stand up...

208
00:24:49.547 --> 00:24:52.608
Fresh pork. reasonable price!

209
00:24:57.522 --> 00:24:59.784
Fresh pork...

210
00:24:59.023 --> 00:25:01.753
Madam.

211
00:25:01.826 --> 00:25:04.851
Come here. madam...
It's great for making soup.

212
00:25:04.995 --> 00:25:06.426
