213
00:25:09.767 --> 00:25:11.756
Two catty (or One Kilogram)
of pork please!

214
00:25:14.739 --> 00:25:15.763
No business with you!

215
00:25:42.800 --> 00:25:43.824
Extra release!

216
00:25:43.901 --> 00:25:45.961
Hercules O'Brien...

217
00:25:46.371 --> 00:25:48.736
32 plays without losing one

218
00:25:48.906 --> 00:25:51.502
25 fighters seriuosly injured.

219
00:25:51.742 --> 00:25:53.607
challenges all Chinese fighters.

220
00:25:53.844 --> 00:25:55.038
Vows to defeat every...

221
00:25:55.446 --> 00:25:56.913
"Sick Man of Asia."

222
00:25:57.314 --> 00:25:59.043
No one dare to callenge him.

223
00:26:02.686 --> 00:26:03.778
Jinsun.

224
00:26:06.557 --> 00:26:07.785
I'm so sorry for what I've done.

225
00:26:08.959 --> 00:26:11.018
I realized my mistakes...

226
00:26:12.496 --> 00:26:13.758
only too late!

227
00:26:15.332 --> 00:26:16.799
It hurts to think about it.

228
00:26:18.903 --> 00:26:20.598
Let's forget about the past.

229
00:26:21.639 --> 00:26:22.901
That chapter is over.

230
00:26:30.481 --> 00:26:31.641
Jinsun...

231
00:26:31.949 --> 00:26:33.507
I don't know how to begin.

232
00:26:33.751 --> 00:26:35.048
