233
00:26:35.986 --> 00:26:37.613
I need to borrow some money.

234
00:26:37.788 --> 00:26:39.915
What? You still want to fight?

235
00:26:40.991 --> 00:26:41.783
Yes.

236
00:26:43.928 --> 00:26:45.691
You cannot go down that path again.

237
00:26:46.063 --> 00:26:47.990
I will not give you any money.

238
00:27:36.981 --> 00:27:37.913
Young Master.

239
00:27:38.916 --> 00:27:39.940
Master Huo.

240
00:27:40.017 --> 00:27:41.985
my master wants you to have this.

241
00:27:46.457 --> 00:27:47.788
Who's your master?

242
00:27:48.092 --> 00:27:50.890
His name is Nong. Nong Jinsun.

