You've received a dinner invitation.

282
00:34:37.100 --> 00:34:38.533
I never dreamed it would be you.

283
00:34:39.303 --> 00:34:41.568
I've been waiting for this day. Yuanjia.

284
00:34:45.275 --> 00:34:46.435
Am I still your friend?

285
00:34:47.444 --> 00:34:49.275
Your friendship... is very important to me.

286
00:34:50.247 --> 00:34:51.305
How can I not?

287
00:34:52.115 --> 00:34:55.516
I always knew that you
would not disappoint me.

288
00:34:57.988 --> 00:34:59.922
But I did. for a long time.

289
00:35:01.358 --> 00:35:03.952
Let's not talk about the past.

290
00:35:04.828 --> 00:35:06.455
Come. have a seat.

291
00:35:08.565 --> 00:35:10.897
Here. your favorite wine.

292
00:35:12.603 --> 00:35:13.433
Come on.

293
00:35:15.439 --> 00:35:16.337
What's the matter?

294
00:35:16.506 --> 00:35:18.940
I stopped drinking. A long time ago.

295
00:35:19.509 --> 00:35:21.443
Why?

296
00:35:21.945 --> 00:35:23.879
But you loved to drink.

297
00:35:24.281 --> 00:35:26.408
I've learned from my mistakes.

298
00:35:29.019 --> 00:35:31.111
That's wonderful.

299
00:35:31.921 --> 00:35:33.355
Let's have tea instead.

300
00:35:42.466 --> 00:35:43.262
Yuanjia.

301
00:35:45.002 --> 00:35:48.870
Your victory gained respect
for all Chinese people.

302
00:35:49.373 --> 00:35:51.900
The foreigners have bullied us
for too long.

303
00:35:52.175 --> 00:35:54.006
Someone should stand up.

304
00:35:54.244 --> 00:35:56.341
If that hadn't happened.
they would have continued to see us

305
00:35:56.480 --> 00:35:57.947
as the sick man of East Asia!

306
00:35:59.016 --> 00:36:00.040
My friend...

307
00:36:00.951 --> 00:36:02.316
I'm really proud of you.

308
00:36:03.153 --> 00:36:04.142
Enjoy!

309
00:36:07.157 --> 00:36:08.351
Chinese must get strengthened.

310
00:36:09.493 --> 00:36:11.085
The Westerners despised us partially

311
00:36:11.895 --> 00:36:13.385
because we've been busy

312
00:36:13.630 --> 00:36:16.030
fighting among ourselves.

313
00:36:16.967 --> 00:36:19.902
That becomes a laughing stock for others.

314
00:36:23.473 --> 00:36:26.033
Foreigners see us as
the sick man of East Asia!

315
00:36:26.576 --> 00:36:28.043
What they call us is irrelevant.

316
00:36:28.979 --> 00:36:29.777
What matters is

317
00:36:29.913 --> 00:36:32.582
if we are really sick.

318
00:36:33.018 --> 00:36:36.986
or. if we are not attempting to cure

319
00:36:37.287 --> 00:36:38.447
the disease even

320
00:36:38.689 --> 00:36:40.384
when we know it is there.

321
00:36:41.324 --> 00:36:43.155
They still flaunt their superiority.

322
00:36:49.399 --> 00:36:53.961
I didn't expect you to be so insightful.

323
00:36:55.472 --> 00:36:58.967
Compared to you. I am kind of bookish.

324
00:37:09.252 --> 00:37:10.184
Jinsun.

325
00:37:10.554 --> 00:37:11.680
when do you return to Tianjin?

326
00:37:12.522 --> 00:37:14.956
I'm going to stay in Shanghai.

327
00:37:16.293 --> 00:37:17.726
Who about your restaurant?

328
00:37:19.529 --> 00:37:20.359
I sold it.

329
00:37:20.430 --> 00:37:21.624
What?

330
00:37:22.332 --> 00:37:23.663
But it was so profitable.

331
00:37:24.434 --> 00:37:26.299
The Jingwu Sports Federation needs...

332
00:37:26.670 --> 00:37:28.399
start-up funds.

333
00:37:31.575 --> 00:37:34.703
But the restaurant has been your life!

334
00:37:35.479 --> 00:37:37.140
My restaurant means little...

335
00:37:37.414 --> 00:37:38.540
compared to...

336
00:37:38.782 --> 00:37:40.443
your vision.

337
00:37:41.384 --> 00:37:42.351
Yuanjia.

338
00:37:42.586 --> 00:37:44.417
I do not know Wushu.

339
00:37:46.022 --> 00:37:49.480
but I do know how to help.

340
00:37:51.595 --> 00:37:52.619
I hope it will be enough.

341
00:37:55.465 --> 00:37:56.432
Jinsun!

342
00:37:57.234 --> 00:37:59.099
I was gone for quite a few years.

343
00:38:00.103 --> 00:38:02.537
Everyday I asked myself

344
00:38:03.140 --> 00:38:05.472
why I learned kung fu.

345
00:38:06.343 --> 00:38:09.779
and whether or not
it was only for fighting.

346
00:38:10.747 --> 00:38:12.305
Have you had an answer?

347
00:38:14.785 --> 00:38:16.184
Only the weak

348
00:38:16.820 --> 00:38:19.687
need to prove their power through force.

349
00:38:21.758 --> 00:38:24.522
but what force leads to

350
00:38:24.594 --> 00:38:26.357
is endless hatred.

351
00:38:27.531 --> 00:38:29.123
I want to change kung fu

352
00:38:29.399 --> 00:38:31.560
into a sport.

353
00:38:32.536 --> 00:38:35.994
with which one can shape oneself
both physically and spiritually.

354
00:38:36.339 --> 00:38:37.465
That's a good idea.

355
00:38:38.542 --> 00:38:40.476
You should let more know about it.

356
00:38:42.412 --> 00:38:44.710
I don't know how much I can achieve.

357
00:38:46.183 --> 00:38:47.514
but I will try my best.

358
00:38:52.756 --> 00:38:54.087
Did you hear that?

359
00:38:55.091 --> 00:38:56.058
Yes.

360
00:38:57.394 --> 00:39:00.386
I heard a voice calling.

361
00:39:02.732 --> 00:39:04.324
Now what we hear

362
00:39:04.601 --> 00:39:06.125
is the same voice!

363
00:39:09.539 --> 00:39:12.770
Jingwu Sports Federation

364
00:39:16.680 --> 00:39:17.510
Yuanjia!

365
00:39:18.816 --> 00:39:19.575
Zhaojian

366
00:39:19.817 --> 00:39:22.049
I was wrong to disrespect you.

367
00:39:22.285 --> 00:39:23.547
Master Huo. I hope that...

368
00:39:24.521 --> 00:39:25.317
I am so glad that you are here.

369
00:39:25.555 --> 00:39:26.817
I was going to pick you up.

370
00:39:27.624 --> 00:39:28.591
Laifu.

371
00:39:28.658 --> 00:39:29.488
Master

372
00:39:29.559 --> 00:39:31.220
would you please show Mr. Zhao around?

373
00:39:35.465 --> 00:39:36.363
Yuanjia!

374
00:39:38.635 --> 00:39:41.399
As we've discussed. the Jingwu Manifesto.

375
00:39:43.638 --> 00:39:42.605
Take a look.

376
00:39:45.575 --> 00:39:48.544
Our motto:

377
00:39:49.212 --> 00:39:51.703
"Body. Mind and Soul".

378
00:39:53.149 --> 00:39:55.549
Wushu is a way to cultivate one's body.
mind and soul.

379
00:39:55.819 --> 00:39:58.550
All Wushu disciplines
are respected equally.

380
00:39:58.888 --> 00:40:00.448
By working together...

381
00:40:02.425 --> 00:40:05.189
We can better ourselves...

382
00:40:05.662 --> 00:40:08.290
and stand strong as one nation

383
00:40:08.598 --> 00:40:11.897
We influence others through...

384
00:40:12.335 --> 00:40:14.702
cooperation. not intimidation.

385
00:40:14.772 --> 00:40:17.103
Through this ideal. we will always...

386
00:40:17.340 --> 00:40:18.568
Stand Strong!

387
00:40:19.776 --> 00:40:21.903
Jingwu Sports Federation 1910

388
00:40:26.950 --> 00:40:28.110
Shanghai Foreign Chamber of Commerce

389
00:40:28.385 --> 00:40:30.818
Well. gentlemen. it's too rich for me.

390
00:40:30.999 --> 00:40:32.154
I only bet on sure things.

391
00:40:34.658 --> 00:40:35.716
Then perhaps you'll be interested...

392
00:40:35.959 --> 00:40:38.689
in joining our little wager against this...

393
00:40:38.929 --> 00:40:40.897
Huo Yuanjia fellow?

394
00:40:41.698 --> 00:40:42.790
He'd better lose this time.

395
00:40:43.199 --> 00:40:46.362
It cost me 6.000 francs
when he beat this O' Brien.

396
00:40:46.736 --> 00:40:48.328
Mr. Mita here...

397
00:40:48.605 --> 00:40:51.597
will ensure that you win back
everything that you lost...

398
00:40:51.808 --> 00:40:53.232
plus a little bit more.

399
00:40:53.576 --> 00:40:56.545
I've suggested a competition
of four matches...

400
00:40:56.646 --> 00:40:59.137
between our countries' best against him.

401
00:40:59.482 --> 00:41:02.883
We beat him and leave
the Chinese with nothing to brag about.

402
00:41:03.286 --> 00:41:04.480
Four against one?

403
00:41:04.788 --> 00:41:07.552
What makes you so sure
he is going to accept that?

404
00:41:07.657 --> 00:41:09.522
Pride? Honor?

405
00:41:09.759 --> 00:41:11.351
The prestige of his school?

406
00:41:11.594 --> 00:41:12.720
It's of no importance.

407
00:41:13.330 --> 00:41:15.264
He has already accepted the challenge.

408
00:41:15.665 --> 00:41:18.156
Then. gentlemen.
I'll take you up on your wager.

409
00:41:18.435 --> 00:41:20.198
And to make it a little more interesting...

410
00:41:20.804 --> 00:41:22.772
I'm going to back the Chinese.

411
00:41:24.341 --> 00:41:27.538
Mita... you are certain Huo Yuanjia will lose?

412
00:41:27.777 --> 00:41:29.642
With what I have in mind...

413
00:41:30.013 --> 00:41:31.878
our victory is guaranteed.

414
00:41:51.768 --> 00:41:52.598
Yuanjia

415
00:41:54.571 --> 00:41:55.663
One of the contestants

416
00:41:55.905 --> 00:41:58.499
Tanaka. the Japanese fighter...

417
00:41:58.775 --> 00:41:59.901
wishes to meet you.

418
00:42:00.510 --> 00:42:03.775
I heard he remains undefeated.
He is one of the best.

419
00:42:06.750 --> 00:42:09.218
Good. one can always learn from the best.

420
00:42:09.786 --> 00:42:12.949
I suspect that the
Foreign Chamber of Commerce...

421
00:42:13.390 --> 00:42:14.687
might have a hidden agenda.

422
00:42:15.025 --> 00:42:15.719
How can they set up...

423
00:42:15.959 --> 00:42:18.519
a 'one against four' contest?

424
00:42:18.962 --> 00:42:19.929
It is...

425
00:42:21.363 --> 00:42:22.923
an attempt to humiliate us.

426
00:42:23.133 --> 00:42:26.632
and undermine our position.

427
00:42:27.904 --> 00:42:28.893
You're right.

428
00:42:29.839 --> 00:42:32.603
One against four is unfair...

429
00:42:32.842 --> 00:42:34.366
plus I have to win each match.

430
00:42:36.513 --> 00:42:37.878
But not everything in life...

431
00:42:38.748 --> 00:42:41.842
is fair.

432
00:42:44.888 --> 00:42:46.549
For the sake of the Federation.

433
00:42:48.691 --> 00:42:49.715
I have no other choice.

434
00:42:50.560 --> 00:42:51.754
What if?

435
00:42:52.896 --> 00:42:56.423
Jinsun.
I want to ask you to do something...

436
00:42:56.666 --> 00:42:57.598
What is it?

437
00:42:58.768 --> 00:43:01.896
After this fight.
you should head the Sports Federation.

438
00:43:02.705 --> 00:43:03.637
Why?

439
00:43:05.842 --> 00:43:08.811
I want to visit Moon and Grandma.

440
00:43:09.512 --> 00:43:10.638
I made a promise.

441
00:43:24.794 --> 00:43:26.386
Do you know anything...

442
00:43:26.830 --> 00:43:28.991
about teas?

443
00:43:31.000 --> 00:43:33.798
I don't really want to know...

444
00:43:34.804 --> 00:43:37.295
because I don't like categories.

445
00:43:37.740 --> 00:43:38.866
Tea is tea.

446
00:43:38.942 --> 00:43:40.842
Each has its own characteristics

447
00:43:41.077 --> 00:43:42.669
hence different grades.

448
00:43:45.615 --> 00:43:48.049
What's the purpose of grading?

449
00:43:49.586 --> 00:43:52.077
All teas are grown in nature...

450
00:43:52.789 --> 00:43:53.983
with little discernable differences

451
00:43:54.858 --> 00:43:56.052
So you really don't know teas.

452
00:43:56.893 --> 00:43:58.827
Once you learn
you can tell the differences.

453
00:43:59.829 --> 00:44:01.091
Maybe you're right.

454
00:44:01.631 --> 00:44:03.462
The way I see it...

455
00:44:03.766 --> 00:44:05.563
the tea does not...

456
00:44:05.802 --> 00:44:07.895
judge itself.

457
00:44:08.171 --> 00:44:09.071
People...

458
00:44:10.540 --> 00:44:12.440
judge the tea.

459
00:44:13.076 --> 00:44:15.010
As for me. I don't want to do that.

460
00:44:15.445 --> 00:44:17.606
Why not?

461
00:44:18.081 --> 00:44:20.049
When you are in a good mood.

462
00:44:20.550 --> 00:44:21.847
the grade of the tea...

463
00:44:22.952 --> 00:44:25.546
does not matter.

464
00:44:26.055 --> 00:44:28.580
I've never seen it that way.

465
00:44:28.825 --> 00:44:32.556
In your opinion.
is one style of Wushu superior...

466
00:44:33.129 --> 00:44:36.826
to another?

467
00:44:37.167 --> 00:44:38.634
I don't think so.

468
00:44:40.036 --> 00:44:42.937
If no particular style is superior...

469
00:44:43.940 --> 00:44:45.874
why have...

470
00:44:46.609 --> 00:44:48.167
so many competitions?

471
00:44:48.912 --> 00:44:49.880
I believe...

472
00:44:50.147 --> 00:44:51.747
no single style is superior.

473
00:44:51.983 --> 00:44:55.577
Only different skill levels.

474
00:44:57.520 --> 00:44:58.953
It is through training that...

475
00:44:59.022 --> 00:45:00.922
one discovers one's strength.

476
00:45:02.091 --> 00:45:04.025
Perhaps. the most formidable...

477
00:45:04.561 --> 00:45:05.960
enemy lies within onself.

478
00:45:06.629 --> 00:45:10.190
Competitions can lead us
to a path of self-discovery?

479
00:45:11.000 --> 00:45:11.864
You mean...

480
00:45:11.935 --> 00:45:12.993
our most important battle...

481
00:45:13.436 --> 00:45:14.801
is actually fought within?

482
00:45:25.715 --> 00:45:26.977
Your words

483
00:45:27.217 --> 00:45:30.084
are poignant.

484
00:45:33.056 --> 00:45:35.047
Let's...

485
00:45:35.458 --> 00:45:38.086
enjoy the tea.

486
00:45:38.728 --> 00:45:41.720
- Please enjoy.
- Thank you.

487
00:47:10.153 --> 00:47:14.055
Shanghai 1910

488
00:47:16.726 --> 00:47:19.923
French Concession Pierre Theatre

489
00:47:22.265 --> 00:47:24.199
The Fight Arena

490
00:47:56.065 --> 00:47:58.625
Today's battle

491
00:47:58.868 --> 00:48:01.701
is between four fighters
from the Foreign Chamber of Commerce

492
00:48:01.938 --> 00:48:04.907
and Huo Yuanjia
of the Jingwu Sports Federation.

493
00:48:14.984 --> 00:48:16.747
Whichever side falls first

494
00:48:16.986 --> 00:48:18.647
or signals to admit defeat

495
00:48:18.888 --> 00:48:21.914
will be considered to have lost the match.

496
00:48:23.793 --> 00:48:25.158
This is unusual.

497
00:48:27.063 --> 00:48:28.826
Four against one?

498
00:48:30.366 --> 00:48:32.095
You never told me.

499
00:48:32.368 --> 00:48:33.926
Both the Chamber of Commerce...

500
00:48:34.170 --> 00:48:36.104
and the Federation agreed.

501
00:48:36.205 --> 00:48:37.399
Don't be concerned.

502
00:48:37.874 --> 00:48:40.001
This is not a competition.

503
00:48:41.344 --> 00:48:42.811
This is murder.

504
00:48:43.045 --> 00:48:45.070
Tanaka. you're overreacting.

505
00:48:45.681 --> 00:48:47.999
Huo Yuanjia fought the best fighters...
from around the world.

506
00:48:48.184 --> 00:48:49.051
and won each time.

507
00:48:49.152 --> 00:48:51.677
The rules... he set them up.

508
00:48:51.921 --> 00:48:53.218
Mita.

509
00:48:55.057 --> 00:48:56.684
What's your deal?

510
00:48:57.827 --> 00:48:59.419
Is this really for the pride of Japan?

511
00:48:59.829 --> 00:49:01.160
Or did you place a large bet?

512
00:49:03.199 --> 00:49:04.757
The spirit Of Wushu...

513
00:49:05.234 --> 00:49:06.895
is the most important thing.

514
00:49:10.239 --> 00:49:12.036
To compete is to win.

515
00:49:12.909 --> 00:49:15.673
Now the first round!
Huo Yuanjia against the British boxer!

516
00:49:20.016 --> 00:49:22.712
British Boxer. Peter Smith

517
00:49:27.790 --> 00:49:28.222
Start!

518
00:50:03.793 --> 00:50:08.785
Belgium Royal Riding Coach. Hanks Herzog

519
00:51:02.318 --> 00:51:03.307
Great job. master!

520
00:51:13.195 --> 00:51:16.221
Fencing champion of Europe. Antony Kasia

521
00:52:23.466 --> 00:52:25.400
This is our embarrassment.
We can't let him win.

522
00:52:35.878 --> 00:52:37.436
The fourth and
final contest will now begin.

523
00:52:37.680 --> 00:52:40.444
The competitor to represent
the Foreign Chamber of Commerce...

524
00:52:40.683 --> 00:52:43.516
is Tanaka from Japan.

525
00:52:47.323 --> 00:52:48.119
Begin!

526
00:52:48.924 --> 00:52:50.084
Yuanjia.

527
00:52:50.426 --> 00:52:53.054
This is an unfair contest.

528
00:52:53.929 --> 00:52:56.659
If you wish to re-schedule...

529
00:52:57.166 --> 00:52:59.066
that's fine with me.

530
00:52:59.635 --> 00:53:01.432
You're very kind.

531
00:53:02.138 --> 00:53:04.003
We started the fight...

532
00:53:04.573 --> 00:53:05.972
we must finish.

533
00:53:07.176 --> 00:53:07.938
Please!

534
00:53:26.062 --> 00:53:26.851
Begin!

535
00:54:36.499 --> 00:54:37.966
Master. that's great!

536
00:55:24.613 --> 00:55:26.444
This round is a draw.

537
00:55:27.082 --> 00:55:29.141
Please set down your weapons. gentlemen...

538
00:55:29.518 --> 00:55:31.418
and prepare for hand-to-hand combat.

539
00:55:35.157 --> 00:55:36.488
Mita. where have you been?

540
00:55:36.859 --> 00:55:38.983
We're going to lose.

541
00:55:39.495 --> 00:55:41.827
Don't worry. gentlemen.
I have it under control.

542
00:56:37.219 --> 00:56:37.776
Yuanjia!

543
00:56:50.933 --> 00:56:52.093
Time out!

544
00:56:52.801 --> 00:56:55.702
- What's going on?
- What is he doing?

545
00:56:59.942 --> 00:57:00.499
Yuanjia!

546
00:57:00.743 --> 00:57:03.211
- Tanaka!
- Go now! Go!

547
00:57:08.417 --> 00:57:09.884
What happened? What happened?

548
00:57:11.186 --> 00:57:11.845
What happened?

549
00:57:12.254 --> 00:57:13.152
Poisoned!

550
00:57:13.389 --> 00:57:15.187
Poison? What poison?

551
00:57:15.625 --> 00:57:17.751
How did this happen?

552
00:57:18.228 --> 00:57:20.661
- What do you need?
- Tea...

553
00:57:20.729 --> 00:57:22.162
Tea!

554
00:57:22.564 --> 00:57:23.588
Where's the teapot?

555
00:57:24.433 --> 00:57:27.630
The tea is laced. But it's gone!

556
00:57:27.870 --> 00:57:30.395
We're going straight to the hospital.

557
00:57:31.707 --> 00:57:34.575
Too late. The toxin is...

558
00:57:35.044 --> 00:57:36.474
in my blood!

559
00:57:36.712 --> 00:57:38.577
Let me take revenge.

560
00:57:41.517 --> 00:57:42.677
Sheng.

561
00:57:44.687 --> 00:57:46.348
We...

562
00:57:47.222 --> 00:57:48.484
must not.

563
00:57:51.727 --> 00:57:52.785
Revenge only...

564
00:57:53.729 --> 00:57:55.697
brings more bloodshed.

565
00:57:57.566 --> 00:57:58.931
No more revenge.

566
00:58:01.770 --> 00:58:05.206
We must strive to better ourselves.

567
00:58:05.441 --> 00:58:08.604
Forget the competition.

568
00:58:08.677 --> 00:58:10.838
We're going to hospital.

569
00:58:14.683 --> 00:58:15.672
Jinsun.

570
00:58:17.219 --> 00:58:18.982
it took me years to understand...

571
00:58:20.956 --> 00:58:24.687
the true meaning of Wushu.

572
00:58:26.662 --> 00:58:28.630
and its purpose.

573
00:58:29.932 --> 00:58:31.797
The competition must continue.

574
00:58:33.302 --> 00:58:34.735
One cannot choose...

575
00:58:34.970 --> 00:58:36.699
how one's life begins.

576
00:58:39.341 --> 00:58:42.777
But one can choose...
to face the end with courage.

577
00:58:48.784 --> 00:58:49.842
Master.

578
00:58:50.319 --> 00:58:52.714
What are you doing?
Finish him off in the next round!

579
00:58:52.955 --> 00:58:54.013
Why do you say that?

580
00:58:55.057 --> 00:58:56.456
It's not for you to decide.

581
00:58:56.692 --> 00:58:57.750
I must win this fight!

582
00:58:57.993 --> 00:58:59.790
Whatever it takes. Just win!

583
00:59:08.704 --> 00:59:10.399
We... Stand strong!

584
00:59:10.639 --> 00:59:13.241
Stand strong! Stand strong!

585
00:59:20.482 --> 00:59:21.449
You really want to win?

586
00:59:42.638 --> 00:59:43.662
Let's stop.

587
00:59:44.339 --> 00:59:46.830
Treasure your life.

588
00:59:49.511 --> 00:59:50.443
Listen to them...

589
00:59:51.947 --> 00:59:53.881
it's not just about me.

590
00:59:59.922 --> 01:00:00.820
If you wish to continue.

591
01:00:01.623 --> 01:00:03.989
I won't hold back.

592
01:00:06.462 --> 01:00:07.759
It is my honor.

593
01:02:10.519 --> 01:02:11.884
Young Master...

594
01:02:13.022 --> 01:02:15.522
He's down! He's down!
Huo Yuanjia's down!

595
01:02:15.824 --> 01:02:18.987
Go! Go! Go!

596
01:02:19.061 --> 01:02:20.619
Make the announcement!

597
01:02:27.169 --> 01:02:28.727
Wait!

598
01:02:51.293 --> 01:02:52.225
Huo...

599
01:02:52.861 --> 01:02:53.056
Yuan... Jia!

600
01:02:53.264 --> 01:02:55.027
Yuanjia!

601
01:02:57.165 --> 01:03:03.602
Huo Yuanjia! Huo Yuanjia!
Huo Yuanjia! Huo Yuanjia!

602
01:03:17.553 --> 01:03:19.042
Tanaka. you son-of-a bitch.

603
01:03:19.288 --> 01:03:20.949
What is this?

604
01:03:21.056 --> 01:03:22.045
I lost!

605
01:03:22.124 --> 01:03:24.024
Who said you lost?

606
01:03:24.259 --> 01:03:26.090
I know it in my heart.

607
01:03:26.528 --> 01:03:27.517
I lost. Fair and square.

608
01:03:28.130 --> 01:03:29.495
Who do you think you are?

609
01:03:29.731 --> 01:03:30.891
You have no right to decide.

610
01:03:30.999 --> 01:03:32.933
You can't be Japanese.

611
01:03:42.077 --> 01:03:45.843
You are a disgrace to Japan!

612
01:03:47.816 --> 01:03:53.521
Huo Yuanjia! Huo Yuanjia!

613
01:05:52.040 --> 01:05:56.875
Huo Yuanjia died from poisoning
at the age of 42.

614
01:05:58.246 --> 01:06:00.146
"The spirit of Wushu" as espoused
by Huo Yuanjia continues to

615
01:06:00.315 --> 01:06:02.240
spread and thrive long
after he passed away...

616
01:06:02.317 --> 01:06:04.342
today. the Jingwu Sports
Federation flourishes around the world.

617
01:06:04.786 --> 01:06:05.718
with branches in over 50 countries.

618
01:06:06.988 --> 01:06:08.785
To commemorate Huo Yuenjia's spirit.

619
01:06:09.024 --> 01:06:10.184
Inscribed by Sun Zhongshan.
Father of the nation

620
01:06:11.693 --> 01:06:14.457
To uphold the spirit of Wushu by Sunwen

621
01:07:17.359 --> 01:07:18.917
Excuse me! Miss. Yang?

622
01:07:19.327 --> 01:07:20.385
What are your chances?

623
01:07:20.829 --> 01:07:22.763
I did my best. That's what's important.

624
01:07:23.031 --> 01:07:24.191
Is it enough?

625
01:07:25.305 --> 01:08:25.810
Do you want subtitles for any video?
